snippet.title: Transformers: Cybertron Adventures (Wii) - Intro (HQ)
snippet.description:
Since I have the .bik videos for the game, I decided to upload what's likely the highest quality version of the intro CG video of the game. Just like the Next Level Games logo animation, the .bik file is also 854x480 resolution!

And here's the original .bik file itself for your viewing pleasure:

https://www.mediafire.com/file/q0xffjsg1tgezzc/intro.bik/file
